gov.loc.repository.bagit.bag

Class CancelTriggeringBagDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.loc.repository.bagit.bag.CancelThresholdBase
      • gov.loc.repository.bagit.bag.CancelTriggeringBagDecorator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bag, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class CancelTriggeringBagDecorator
extends CancelThresholdBase
implements Bag
    A decorator for Bag that keeps an internal count of method accesses, and calls the cancel method on a given object when the given threshold is exceeded. Used for unit testing.
    Version:
    $Id$
